content: That's fantastic to hear! I'm glad that setting boundaries and seeking support is helping you feel more empowered. Remember, you're taking a brave step towards putting your well-being first, and that's an essential part of personal growth. Take your time, and don't rush the process of ending the toxic relationship. I'm here to offer support and encourage you every step of the way. Keep up the good work, and don't hesitate to reach out if you need someone to talk to.
